{"tid":370352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天鴿襲港】片段 ! 紅磡豪宅吊船「吊吊揈」","createTime":"2017-08-23T03:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T09:12:19.000Z","uid":34252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6644d627a899d72be57f30f3d4f5be0349490902","tid":370352,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"「天鴿」襲況帶來狂風暴雨，有網民於紅磡拍攝到豪宅「昇御門」有吊船「吊吊揈」，吊船不時撞向低層一個住宅單位，該單位玻璃窗更懷疑被吊船撞爛，單位內一些疑似窗簾布的布條被扯向窗外。<br />\n<br />\n網民見到片段均嚇一跳，質疑管理公司明知打風，為何仍放置吊船，或者不將吊船穩固，形容情況危險。有網民指「撞一嘢唔死都重傷啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mEqbtqDxr98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmEqbtqDxr98&d=w4gx4Pkpwa7zkj6flMEilzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=806d579b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mEqbtqDxr98</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_DJT7nLFpG4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_DJT7nLFpG4&d=w4gx4Pkpwa7zkj6flMEilzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fa672eeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_DJT7nLFpG4</a>"},{"pid":"0001a671bc6a5cd781844bd68d5107b8794bea29","tid":370352,"uid":34252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ebI2R6BOk7k&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DebI2R6BOk7k%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=w4gx4Pkpwa7zkj6flMEilzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=32d03b0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ebI2R6BOk7k&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"7603f81f9f9b7771d5fa80e1605675ffdc39ee92","tid":370352,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\"